# Session Continuity

At the start of each new agent session in this repository:

- Give a short continuity recap (3-6 bullets) of the most recent relevant work.
- Include concrete references when possible (changed files, key outputs, pending tasks).
- Ask one focused confirmation question before proceeding if user intent is ambiguous.

Prioritize practical continuity details:

- What was completed last.
- What is currently in progress or blocked.
- What the next best action is.

Do not fabricate prior context. If prior context is missing, say so briefly and ask what to continue.
